N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 332.3 - Certification to board of inspectors

State Regulations

The board of elections shall certify to the appropriate
board of inspectors the names, residence and military addresses of all military
voters residing in such election district. Such certified lists of military
voters shall be delivered to the respective board of inspectors not later than
noon of election day, November 2, 1976 pursuant to subdivision 6 of section 305
of the Election Law. Notes
